Package de.feu.massim22.group3.map

Class MapCellReport

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.map.MapCellReport
public class MapCellReport extends Object
The Class MapCellReport stores information of the current state of a Cell in the vision of an agent.
Author:
Heinz Stadler
